com.biorecorder.edflib.filters

Class EdfFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.biorecorder.edflib.base.EdfWriter
      • com.biorecorder.edflib.filters.EdfFilter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EdfJoiner, EdfSignalsFilter, EdfSignalsRemover

    public class EdfFilter
extends EdfWriter
    A base decorator class (pattern Decorator) that is actually just a wrapper around some other EdfWriter object. It implements the same interface but permits to add some additional functionality to the underlying class.

    EdfFilter itself simply overrides all methods of EdfWriter with versions that pass all requests to the underlying EdfWriter. The only purpose of this class is to be a superclass for real realisation of EdfFilter which normally modify incoming DataRecords before pass (write) them to underlying writer.

    Full analog of FilterOutputStream
